nodes.text: The Trade Federation Hulk was a heap of debris of a Trade Federation ship in the Naboo system.

This hulk standed as a reminder of Naboo's ancient battle against the forces of greed and a monument to the Royal Security Force's prowess in starfighter combat. Even still, rare members of the Trade Federation still lived at the site and were often left alone.
A Trade Federation Outpost was also located in this region.
